---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Financial Disclaimer - BitcoinForWifi">
	<section class="py-20">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
						<span class="gradient-text">Financial Disclaimer</span>
					</h1>
					<p class="text-gray-300 text-lg">
						Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-red-900/20 border border-red-500 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
					<div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v6z"/>
						</svg>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-red-400 font-bold text-lg mb-2">⚠️ IMPORTANT WARNING</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-300">
								This disclaimer is legally binding. Read it carefully before using this website or making any financial decisions.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
					<h2>No Financial Advice</h2>
					<p>
						<strong>BitcoinForWifi is NOT a financial advisor, broker, dealer, or investment advisor.</strong> All content, materials, information, and data provided on this website are for educational and informational purposes only and should not be considered as financial advice, investment advice, trading advice, or any other type of advice.
					</p>
					<p>
						Nothing contained on this website constitutes a solicitation, recommendation, endorsement, or offer by BitcoinForWifi or any third party service provider to buy or sell any securities, cryptocurrencies, or other financial instruments.
					</p>

					<h2>High Risk Warning</h2>
					<p>
						<strong>CRYPTOCURRENCY TRADING AND INVESTMENT INVOLVE EXTREME RISK AND CAN RESULT IN THE LOSS OF YOUR ENTIRE INVESTMENT.</strong> Cryptocurrency markets are highly volatile and speculative. Prices can fluctuate dramatically in short periods.
					</p>
					<p>Risks include but are not limited to:</p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Market Volatility:</strong> Cryptocurrency prices can change rapidly and unpredictably</li>
						<li><strong>Regulatory Risk:</strong> Government regulations can impact cryptocurrency values and legality</li>
						<li><strong>Security Risk:</strong> Exchanges can be hacked; wallets can be compromised</li>
						<li><strong>Liquidity Risk:</strong> Some cryptocurrencies may have limited market liquidity</li>
						<li><strong>Technology Risk:</strong> Blockchain technology may have vulnerabilities or fail</li>
						<li><strong>Counterparty Risk:</strong> Third-party services may fail or be fraudulent</li>
					</ul>

					<h2>No Professional Advice</h2>
					<p>
						The content on Bitcoin Blog is created by individuals who may or may not be certified financial professionals. The authors and publishers of this website are not licensed financial advisors and do not provide personalized investment advice.
					</p>
					<p>
						You should not make any investment decision based solely on the information provided on this website. Before making any investment decisions, you should consult with a qualified financial advisor, tax advisor, or legal counsel.
					</p>

					<h2>Past Performance Disclaimer</h2>
					<p>
						<strong>PAST PERFORMANCE IS NOT INDICATIVE OF FUTURE RESULTS.</strong> Historical returns, expected returns, or probability projections may not reflect actual future performance. Any investment involves substantial risk, including the possible loss of principal.
					</p>
					<p>
						No representation is being made that any account will or is likely to achieve profits or losses similar to those shown. There are numerous factors related to the markets in general or to the implementation of any specific trading program which cannot be fully accounted for in the preparation of hypothetical performance results.
					</p>

