						Information may contain errors, omissions, or become outdated. We are not obligated to update or correct any information. You should independently verify all information before making any decisions.
					</p>

					<h2>No Endorsement</h2>
					<p>
						Reference to any specific cryptocurrency, exchange, product, or service does not constitute an endorsement or recommendation by Bitcoin Blog. We are not responsible for the actions of any third-party platforms or services mentioned on this website.
					</p>

					<h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
