						<li>Conduct thorough research and due diligence</li>
						<li>Understand the technology and risks involved</li>
						<li>Consult with qualified financial and tax professionals</li>
						<li>Only invest what you can afford to lose completely</li>
						<li>Consider your financial situation and risk tolerance</li>
						<li>Understand the legal and tax implications in your jurisdiction</li>
					</ol>

					<h2>No Warranty</h2>
					<p>
						Bitcoin Blog provides all content "AS IS" without any warranties, express or implied. We disclaim all warranties, including but not limited to:
					</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Implied warranties of merchantability</li>
						<li>Implied warranties of fitness for a particular purpose</li>
						<li>Warranties of non-infringement</li>
						<li>Warranties of title or quiet enjoyment</li>
					</ul>

